You missed the small but important fact that Prowl is kinda flying 40 feet or 
so up in the air, Carnage, but we can say he was on the ground.

::Oblitertron/Prowl::

Prowl's eyes widen as he sees the Oblitercons combine. That was the one thing 
he hadn't wanted to happen; the giant Alliance gestalt caused too much death 
and destruction.

A shadow covers Prowl as Dinobot runs up to him, mechfluid spraying over 
Prowl as Dinobot is hit. He swears, glancing back at Oblitertron as another 
shadow passes over him, this one of Oblitertron's foot.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Oblitertron laughs as Dinobot is hit with his optic lasers, bringing a foot 
down on the two bots. Before the foot has a chance to hit either of them, 
though, a tail smashes into Oblitertron's head, the bot stubling to the side, 
his foot missing the Maximals by a few feet.

He spins around, firing his rifle and optic lasers at Necromancer.
